query:
SELECT 
                id AS "id!",
                name AS "name!",
                login AS "login!",
                color AS "color!",
                image AS "image!",
                total_chatter AS "total_chatter!",
                total_channel AS "total_channel!",
                ranking AS "ranking!",
                (
                    SELECT COUNT (*) 
                    FROM ranked_scores_view_per_channel 
                    WHERE channel_id = id
                ) as "total_scores!",
                created_at AS "created_at!",
                updated_at AS "updated_at!"
            FROM channel_leaderboard
            ORDER BY ranking ASC
            LIMIT $1 OFFSET $2
